version_description: Your search options just got a bit better. Now on your map view, you'll notice that each place's pin is colored to match its rating!  Find the best spot to go, quicker.

This release has a few bug fixes here and there, and a few magic mystery things we're testing out behind the scenes.

Have you been somewhere great lately? Make sure to pay it forward and leave a tip to help out the greater community. Others will want to hear about that juicy cheeseburger, outdoor seating, and fancy lavender lemonade that you enjoyed.

Head over to your profile for something new! You'll now find a home for all of the great photos you take at the top of your screen. Your avocado toasts, your scenic lookout views, your #friescoveredwithstuff and more.

While you're looking through your gallery, feel free to tag what's in the photo or write a tip to leave at the place where the photo was taken. Especially if it's a super cheesy ooey gooey slice of perfect pizza. (Sorry, we're very hungry over here.)

Oh hi, didn't see you there. We're just here working on our new look for Fall.

Get ready, because this next update will be a big one...
Ok, we lied. One more update before the big one.

This one goes to 11...

Our ALL-NEW place pages will help you really *experience* somewhere before you decide to go there.

Everything is broken down into Highlights, Info, Photos, and Tips.
•Want to see the most important details of a place? Boom. Highlights tab.
•Is this place open late? Can you bring your dog? Boom. Info tab.
•Want to take a peek around? Drool over food pics? Boom. Photos tab.
•What should you do when you get there? Boom. Tips tab.

Finding the perfect place to go should be easy. And now it is.

So next time you're elected by family and friends to pick a spot to go for dinner, plan a day at the park, or heck, even choose a movie theatre, just open up your trusty City Guide app. Everyone will be happy. You will be the hero. Your loved ones will crowd surf you out of there (probably).

We’ve fixed a few tiny bugs with this release... but if you haven’t yet, you should really check out our all new place pages! They make finding the best spot to go even easier. (And they’re really quite pretty, if we do say so ourselves.)

Mostly behind the scenes stuff in this release. See ya with some new things in the new year!

Great news! Collaborative lists have made their way to mobile! Invite others to add places to your lists and keep everywhere you want to go organized.

Perfect for an upcoming trip with a pal, a neighborhood to-do with a partner or all of the pizza places you and your brother want to hit up the next time he comes to visit you.

Now you can plan better, together.
